## Decision Tree

**Where to put information?**

```
Implementation details → patch.md
Test results → verify.md (ONLY source of truth)
Storybook steps → Storybook story description OR patch.md (Storybook Validation section)
Release notes / status update → Lock doc OR patch.md (System Status Update section)
Targets / Expected behavior → patch.md (embedded sections)
Canonical system docs → Only if SYSTEM_UPDATE (count toward cap)
```

**Decision flow:**

1. Is this test execution/result? → `verify.md` ONLY
2. Is this implementation detail? → `patch.md` (embed as section)
3. Is this canonical system doc? → Only if SYSTEM_UPDATE, count toward cap
4. Would this create >2 files (or >4 for SYSTEM_UPDATE)? → Consolidate into existing files

